    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770206845</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">To Market To Market</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Zum Markt Zum Markt</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Au Marché Au Marché</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ao Mercado Ao Mercado</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Al Mercato Al Mercato</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Στην αγορά στην αγορά</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Al Mercado Al Mercado</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">helps students sharpen their observation and interpretation skills by inviting them to examine images from the turn of the centuries, circa 1900 and circa 2000.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Hilfen Kursteilnehmer schärfen ihre Beobachtung 
und Deutung Fähigkeiten, indem sie sie einladen, Bilder von der 
Umdrehung der Jahrhunderte, des circa 1900 und des circa 2000 zu 
überprüfen.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">les étudiants d'aides affilent leurs 
qualifications d'observation et de traduction en les invitant à 
examiner des images du tour des siècles, du circa 1900 et du circa 
2000.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">os estudantes das ajudas sharpen suas habilidades 
da observação e da interpretação convidando as examinar imagens da
volta dos séculos, do circa 1900 e do circa 2000.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">gli allievi di aiuti affilano le loro abilità di 
interpretazione e di osservazione invitandole ad esaminare le immagini
dalla girata dei secoli, del circa 1900 e del circa 2000.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">βοηθά τους σπουδαστές να ακονίσουν τις δεξιότητές 
τους παρατήρησης και ερμηνείας με την πρόσκληση τους για να 
εξετάσει τις εικόνες από τη στροφή των αιώνων, του circa το 
1900 και του circa το 2000.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">los estudiantes de las ayudas afilan sus 
habilidades de la observación y de la interpretación invitándoles a
que examinen imágenes de la vuelta de los siglos, del circa 1900 y 
del circa 2000.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciências Sociais</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Scienze Sociali</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Κοινωνικές επιστήμες</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencias Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
